productReviews.reviewText: This Cotton works certainly well. It accidentally improves my baseball by a lot.
My Shih-Tzu loves to play with it.
My neighbor Fannie has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks spiky.
My neighbor Zoa has one of these. She works as a scribe and she says it looks wide.
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
